![dict.gif](https://cdn.hashnode.com/res/hashnode/image/upload/v1627366344193/We_heehuL.gif)


![image.png](https://cdn.hashnode.com/res/hashnode/image/upload/v1627365131696/YH8Vaqoh_.png)


